### ─── Variables ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token   = REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN_FROM_LOGIN

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AUTH
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Register admin (secret must match JWT_SECRET in .env)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "yourpassword",
  "secret": "REPLACE_WITH_JWT_SECRET"
}

###

### Login → copy the token into @token above
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "yourpassword"
}

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### HERO
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get hero content
GET {{baseUrl}}/hero

###

### Create hero content (protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/hero
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "label": "New Album",
  "albumTitle": "Blue Boy",
  "ctaText": "Listen Now",
  "ctaUrl": "https://open.spotify.com/album/example"
}

###

### Update hero content (protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/hero
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "label": "Latest Drop",
  "albumTitle": "Blue Boy",
  "ctaText": "Stream Now",
  "ctaUrl": "https://open.spotify.com/album/example"
}

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### RELEASES
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all releases
GET {{baseUrl}}/releases

###

### Get featured releases only
GET {{baseUrl}}/releases?featured=true

###

### Get shelf (non-featured) releases
GET {{baseUrl}}/releases?featured=false

###

### Get single release by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/releases/REPLACE_WITH_RELEASE_ID

###

### Create release (protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/releases
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Blue Boy",
  "eyebrow": "Out Now",
  "featuredArtist": null,
  "coverUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/example/image.jpg",
  "listenUrl": "https://open.spotify.com/album/example",
  "watchUrl": null,
  "featured": true,
  "displayOrder": 1,
  "type": "album"
}

###

### Update release (protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/releases/REPLACE_WITH_RELEASE_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "featured": false,
  "displayOrder": 2
}

###

### Delete release (protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/releases/REPLACE_WITH_RELEASE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### VIDEOS
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/videos

###

### Get single video by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/videos/REPLACE_WITH_VIDEO_ID

###

### Create video (protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/videos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Blue Boy - Official Music Video",
  "thumbnailUrl": "https://img.youtube.com/vi/VIDEOID/maxresdefault.jpg",
  "youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VIDEOID",
  "displayOrder": 1
}

###

### Update video (protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/videos/REPLACE_WITH_VIDEO_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "displayOrder": 2
}

###

### Delete video (protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/videos/REPLACE_WITH_VIDEO_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### TOUR DATES
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get upcoming tour dates
GET {{baseUrl}}/tour-dates

###

### Create tour date (protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tour-dates
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "date": "2026-07-15T20:00:00.000Z",
  "city": "Lagos",
  "venue": "Eko Convention Centre",
  "ticketUrl": "https://tickets.example.com/blueboy-lagos",
  "soldOut": false
}

###

### Update tour date (protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tour-dates/REPLACE_WITH_TOURDATE_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "soldOut": true
}

###

### Delete tour date (protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tour-dates/REPLACE_WITH_TOURDATE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### UPLOADS  (multipart/form-data — use REST Client's file syntax)
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Upload image to Cloudinary (protected)
### Replace the file path with an actual image on your machine
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< C:/Users/Thomson/Pictures/cover.jpg
------Boundary--
